      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Benjamita Behrni redseja/ ka tee kanti tappe/ tad atstahje Israëta Behrni teem Benjamitereem Weetu/ jo tee palaidahs us teem/ kas no pak-katenes fleppeni turrejahs/ ko tee prett Gibeju bij eelikfuschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee/ kas fleppeni tur-rejahs/ steidsehs/ un zehlahs preek-fcha prett Gibeju/ tee/ kas flep-peni turrejahs (fakku es) nahze preekfcha/un kawe wiſfuPilsfah-tu ar Sohbina Afimint.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un teem Israëta Wihreem bija weens norunnahts Laiks ar teem/ kas fleppeni turrejahs/ ka teem bij dauds Duhmus darriht/ un tohs liktu uskahpt no ta Pils-fahta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tä atgreesahs tee Israëta Wihri mo Kauschanas/ un Ben-jamins bij cesahzis kaut un ee-watnoht no teem Israëta Wih-reem kahdus trihsdefinits Wih-rus/ jo tee fazzia: tee irr wiſſit kauti muhfu Preekschä/ lihds ka pirinä Kauschanä.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fahze tee Duhmi no ta Pilsfakta zeltees/ itt ka weens Duhmu-Stabs/ kad nu Benja-mins atpakkat skattijahs/ reds/ tad uszehlahs wiſa Pilsfakta (Ugguns) prett Debbes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Israëta Wihri at-greesahs/ bet Benjamita Wihri istruhzinnajahs/ jo tee redseja to Yaunumu paschus aisneimmam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tä atgreesahs tee preeksch Israëta Behrueem us to Tukme-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "fes Zelfu/ bet tee Raiveji dsin-nahs teem pakkat/ un kas no teen-zitteem Pilsfahteem btj atnahku-chi/ tohs apkaive tee starp fei-tur eekfcha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee nahze apkahrt Ben-jaminu/ tee dsinnahs tam pakka-lihds Menukas/ un faminne toh-lihds Gibejas Preekschu / pre-Saules Uslehfschann.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Benjamita kritta-stozpadefmits tuhksfochi Wil-ri/ schee wiſſi bija stipri Wilri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tä atgreesahs winxt/ u-behdse us to Tuksnefi/ us to A-mina-Kalnu Rimmou/ un te-kawe teem us Zelfeem pa-kat dsihdanees peeztuhkstofchu-Wihrus/ un dsinnahs teem pa-kat lihds Gideomain / un kan-wehl no teem diwituhkstofchu-Wihrus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tä bija wiſſi/ kas t-Deenä no Benjamita kritte d-widefmits un peeztuhkstof-Wihri/ kas to Sohbinn iswile-schee wiſſi bija stipri Wilri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 47,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet feszchfimts Wihi-greesahs/ nn behdse Tuksnefi u-to Akmixa-Kalna Rimmnon/ u-palikke eekſch ta Akmixa-Kaln-Rimmnon tfchetr Mehneschus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 48,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Israëta Behrut a-greesahs us Benjamita Beh-neem/ un kawe tohs ar Sohbina-Afimint eekſch Pilsfakta/ tik la-bt Wihrus/ ka Lohpus/ un wiſſi-kas atrasts tappe/ tee eedeďsinaj-arridsan wiſſus Pilstahtus a-Ugguni/ ko tee atradde.\n"
    }
  ],
